\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces LLaDA-8B / MBPP: KMeans silhouette on the top-20 fail-enriched features (solid) vs.\ permutation null mean (dashed) across denoising steps. The gold band marks the SAE training noise range ($\mathrm  {dlm\_t}\!\in \![0.05,0.5]\!\approx \!$ step 64--122). The signal-to-null gap is $\!\le \!0$ at steps 0--16, jumps to $+0.18$ at step 32, peaks at $+0.31$ at step 64 (the only step with $p{<}0.05$, marked with a star), and falls back to $+0.18$ at step 127.}}{2}{figure.caption.9}\protected@file@percent }
