\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Trajectory shape replicates across condition. Each panel plots observed silhouette and permutation null mean across denoising steps. \emph  {Left} (LLaDA-8B / MBPP) and \emph  {middle} (Dream-7B / MBPP): peak at step 64, post-peak fall-back; Dream's signal collapses below null at step 127. \emph  {Right} (LLaDA-8B / JSON schema): step-64 peak plus an additional early-formation shoulder at steps 4--16, paralleling the probe paper's structural-vs-reasoning split.}}{3}{figure.caption.11}\protected@file@percent }
